				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": " Zrell 'greets' the player inside the Tower along with the rest of the Monnrise offencive force during the assault on Moonrise. Nightsong might be alive or dead.\r\n\r\nThis is a stand-off - she's protecting the tower, and the players are attacking. Z'rell is confident that she'll put the players and their allies down here, and shows no fear."
